title: I have the ROUNDED app in SYSTEM applied 5 times but only 1 is active. I can't disable any
content:
I went into my system apps and found the ROUNDED app installed 5 times. Only 1 is operating. I can't disable the ones that aren't working. 

I fear this could lead to some major issues.

I have had a few issues but it feels like I got a corrupt update at one time
